# Audio assets — license note (exception to the repo's MIT license)

The music in this directory and in `/soundtrack` was **composed for this project** by
arranging royalty-free sample loops that the project author licensed through
**Splice** (splice.com) and **Zenhiser**. Under those sample licenses, the resulting
musical works may be used and distributed as part of this game and its soundtrack.

**These rendered tracks are NOT covered by the repository's MIT license** and are
**not** offered for independent reuse. Specifically, you may **not** extract, re-use,
or redistribute these files (or any stems/loops derived from them) as samples, loops,
or as part of any sample library or competing product. They are bundled solely to be
played within this game and heard as its soundtrack.

The **raw source sample loops are never included** in this repository — only the
finished, multi-layer arrangements.

If you fork this project for your own release, replace these files with your own
licensed or original music.

*Proudly Made in Nebraska. Go Big Red! 🌽 <https://xkcd.com/2347/>*
